    ('cat_high_contrast_cards', 3, 3, 'visible', true, true, 'Most comprehensive set with staged learning', 'beiens Newborn Essentials Sensory Toys Cards, 160 Page Black White Visual Stimulation Learning Activity Cards', 'beiens', 'Amazon UK', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/beiens-Contrast-Flashcard-Stimulation-Educational/dp/B07WZT8DTD', NULL, 'GBP 13.99', 'in_stock', NULL, 'An extensive set of 160-page black and white visual stimulation cards designed for babies aged 0-36 months, with staged learning for different developmental phases. Features anti-glare surface and eco-friendly ink.', 'This product stands out for its sheer volume of cards and staged approach to visual development, covering a wide age range. The exceptionally high number of positive reviews on Amazon UK provides strong retail proof of its effectiveness and popularity among parents. The anti-glare and eco-friendly features are also positive attributes.', 'This product stands out for its sheer volume of cards and staged approach to visual development, covering a wide age range. The exceptionally high number of positive reviews on Amazon UK provides strong retail proof of its effectiveness and popularity among parents. The anti-glare and eco-friendly features are also positive attributes.', NULL, NULL, true, 'Good gift', NULL, NULL, NULL, ARRAY[]::text[], 'none'),
